KNOWN BUGS
----------
- duplicate images create problems with the HTML export
- dubious network transparency


For release 1.0.0
-----------------
(in no particular order)

- choice of different website templates
- Undo and Redo
- useful information added to the status bar
- loading thumbnails from a common shared cache
- customize sizes for final images and thumbnails
- provide the choice of a binary file format for .kalbum
- configuration for changing slide image and other options
- image Properties: Colour Correction, open an external editor
- create drop shadows for thumbnails and images
- add a bookshelf manager for an album collection
- documentation
